{"tid":1136682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【法援跟進】聯合醫院刺穿動脈 中風少女奇蹟好轉","createTime":"2019-05-03T07:29:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T14:12:50.000Z","uid":130626,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"412192480aa97d569e88d9a272d3fac301f10f46","tid":1136682,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:29:26.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】一名16歲少女17年11月因橫貫性脊髓炎，在觀塘聯合醫院接受洗血治療，期間醫生將插入靜脈的導管刺穿動脈，導致腦中風，左半身不遂。事隔一年半後，少女情況日漸好轉，其兄長早上在一電台節目中談及妹妹近況時，以「意料之外的奇蹟」來形容其康復情況，指她精神不錯，能簡單交談表達自己和坐起來。<br />\n兄長指，妹妹說話速度較慢，且暫未能如常行走，正展開康復治療，預料治療時間將長達數年甚至以10年計。他特別感激善心人的捐助，讓妹妹得以接受額外治療，加速康復進度。他並透露已獲批法援，將循法律途徑跟進事件。<br />\n兄長還表示，妹妹希望回家休養，但現時家居情況難以配合，如廁所太細等，希望政府酌情讓他們<span style=\"color: red;\">更換較大單位</span>，方便使用輪椅。<br />\n醫院去年公布的檢討報告認為問題不涉及人為疏忽。醫管局兒科中央統籌委員會副主席蘇景桓去年曾向少女家屬表示歉意，但指醫生行為合乎標準，相信不涉及人為疏忽。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vcWZfX1WryQS52JBuAj87w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190503a125742.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FvcWZfX1WryQS52JBuAj87w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190503a125742.jpg&h=85158799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%95%E6%8F%B4%E8%B7%9F%E9%80%B2-%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E5%88%BA%E7%A9%BF%E5%8B%95%E8%84%88-%E4%B8%AD%E9%A2%A8%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%A5%87%E8%B9%9F%E5%A5%BD%E8%BD%89-045600607.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%258F%25B4%25E8%25B7%259F%25E9%2580%25B2-%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2588%25BA%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%2584%2588-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25A5%2587%25E8%25B9%259F%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E8%25BD%2589-045600607.html&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjOSCO5RJLUOM1IbOSdmZk8c%3D&h=433fcbf4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%95%E6%8F%B4%E8%B7%9F%E9%80%B2-%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E5%88%BA%E7%A9%BF%E5%8B%95%E8%84%88-%E4%B8%AD%E9%A2%A8%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%A5%87%E8%B9%9F%E5%A5%BD%E8%BD%89-045600607.html</a>"},{"pid":"8026f7ef37f478f25e582ddb08c6045f790b7226","tid":1136682,"uid":9193,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"聯合醫院賠償未？"},{"pid":"5c987a177c9910afae6d7f19e832e2be91acad07","tid":1136682,"uid":137220,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:37:12.000Z","msg":"其實，呢個係風險，唔係錯誤"},{"pid":"b5286444457070595e2c803831160420b4ba69d6","tid":1136682,"uid":4420,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"5c987a177c9910afae6d7f19e832e2be91acad07","tid":1136682,"uid":137220,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:37:12.000Z","msg":"其實，呢個係風險，唔係錯誤"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:38:38.000Z","msg":"話之你<br />\n總之我要換大屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c751647ec42a80a09b2ad82e25d155accf2fa9df","tid":1136682,"uid":180302,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:39:14.000Z","msg":"好合理 有需要就應該換大單位比佢"},{"pid":"fa36d3d7e433e88b4d28f0202dbb4abb1cd53a9e","tid":1136682,"uid":54437,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:39:49.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為係刺穿動脈令佢奇蹟好轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f307083f65b9a58a84f1153b922b826bb44622f3","tid":1136682,"uid":20325,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5c987a177c9910afae6d7f19e832e2be91acad07","tid":1136682,"uid":137220,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:37:12.000Z","msg":"其實，呢個係風險，唔係錯誤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T07:42:51.000Z","msg":"但之後冇follow up 好耐先發現，就係錯誤"},{"pid":"0424f5a0b01235fe661c97d6a45f2ea7b80b2658","tid":1136682,"uid":34466,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy